WEBVTT

00:09.810 --> 00:11.212
- * ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR

00:11.245 --> 00:13.147
* ONE, TWO, THREE,
FOUR, FIVE, SIX *

00:13.181 --> 00:14.382
* SHAKE IT, DUDE

00:14.415 --> 00:22.390
*

00:28.396 --> 00:29.697
* ONE, TWO, DO IT

00:29.730 --> 00:32.100
*

00:32.133 --> 00:33.534
* ONE, TWO, THREE

00:33.567 --> 00:35.303
- * FOUR, FOUR

00:35.336 --> 00:38.406
*

00:39.840 --> 00:42.810
- [gasping]

01:20.281 --> 01:23.251
[energetic dance music]

01:23.284 --> 01:31.225
*

01:41.802 --> 01:43.871
- HAVEN'T SEEN BRIAN.

01:43.904 --> 01:46.674
- HE'S WITH JUSTIN.
IT'S DATE NIGHT.

01:46.707 --> 01:49.743
- WHOO-HOO.
- [yawns]

01:49.777 --> 01:51.912
- I'M SORRY,
ARE WE KEEPING YOU UP?

01:51.945 --> 01:56.284
- NO.
IT'S THE BUSINESS.

01:56.317 --> 01:57.718
TOILING AWAY,
DAY AND NIGHT,

01:57.751 --> 01:58.752
IT'S NOT THE SAME
AS PUNCHING IN

01:58.786 --> 02:01.189
9:00 TO 6:00
AT WERTSHAFTER'S.

02:01.222 --> 02:04.658
- BUT JUST THINK,
YOU'RE A SUCCESS.

02:04.692 --> 02:06.894
- NOT THAT I'VE HAD MUCH TIME
TO ENJOY IT.

02:06.927 --> 02:09.797
- WHAT YOU NEED IS SOMETHING
TO KEEP YOUR EYELIDS OPEN.

02:09.830 --> 02:13.501
- YEAH, LIKE HIM.
[growls]

02:13.534 --> 02:14.735
- YEAH, RIGHT.

02:14.768 --> 02:15.903
AS IF A NORSE GOD

02:15.936 --> 02:17.771
IS GOING TO BE
INTERESTED IN ME.

02:17.805 --> 02:22.576
- YOU NEVER KNOW
UNLESS YOU TRY.

02:22.610 --> 02:23.777
- SURE, WHAT THE HELL?

02:23.811 --> 02:26.647
I'M TOO TIRED TO CARE.

02:26.680 --> 02:28.349
- ATTABOY.
- YEAH.

02:33.754 --> 02:36.690
- HI. HOW'S IT GOING?

02:38.426 --> 02:40.561
I'M TED.

02:43.564 --> 02:47.735
MAYBE YOU COULD USE IT
AS A BOOKMARK OR SOMETHING.

02:47.768 --> 02:48.936
- [mouthing silently]

02:48.969 --> 02:51.905
- JERKATWORK.NET.

02:51.939 --> 02:54.308
THAT YOU?
- THAT'S RIGHT.

02:54.342 --> 02:56.277
I'M THE PRESIDENT.

02:56.310 --> 02:59.480
- I'M THOR.
- * DON'T JUST STARE

02:59.513 --> 03:02.550
- SO HOW ABOUT HOOKING UP?
- * DANCE WITH ME

03:02.583 --> 03:03.684
- YOU AND ME?

03:03.717 --> 03:07.555
- * DON'T JUST STARE

03:07.588 --> 03:09.823
* DANCE WITH ME
- YOU GOT IT...

03:09.857 --> 03:14.862
THOR.
- * DON'T JUST STARE

03:14.895 --> 03:17.898
* DANCE WITH ME

03:17.931 --> 03:19.567
- HE GAVE YOU HIS NUMBER?

03:19.600 --> 03:23.271
- SEEMS SUCCESS
IS THE ULTIMATE APHRODISIAC.

03:25.339 --> 03:28.509
- OH, SHIT!

03:28.542 --> 03:30.844
- WELL, IF IT ISN'T
THE HUNKIEST PROFESSOR

03:30.878 --> 03:32.680
IN THE WHOLE WIDE WORLD.

03:32.713 --> 03:35.416
- THANK YOU FOR MAKING ME
FEEL SO MUCH BETTER.

03:35.449 --> 03:37.451
- YOU DID THE RIGHT THING.

03:37.485 --> 03:38.619
THE GUY'S POSITIVE.

03:38.652 --> 03:41.622
- POSITIVELY YUMMY.

03:41.655 --> 03:43.424
- THERE ARE PLENTY
OF FUCKABLE GUYS OUT THERE

03:43.457 --> 03:44.758
THAT YOU DON'T HAVE
TO WORRY ABOUT.

03:44.792 --> 03:47.328
- COME ON, LET'S DANCE.

03:47.361 --> 03:49.797
- * FEEL THE HEAT

03:49.830 --> 03:52.400
* FEEL THE MOMENT
FEEL THE BEAT *

03:52.433 --> 03:55.469
* FEEL THE PASSION
FEEL THE HEAT *

03:55.503 --> 03:58.606
*

03:58.639 --> 04:00.741
- IT'S TRUE, THERE'S A LOT
OF FUCKABLE GUYS OUT THERE,

04:00.774 --> 04:02.876
AND I'VE EVEN DATED A FEW.

04:02.910 --> 04:04.878
MORE THAN A FEW.

04:04.912 --> 04:06.013
THE ONLY PROBLEM IS...

04:06.046 --> 04:08.015
THEY'RE NOT BEN.

04:08.048 --> 04:09.417
I CAN'T STOP THINKING
ABOUT HIM.

04:09.450 --> 04:10.751
I'M OBSESSED.
- AND I'M...

04:10.784 --> 04:12.320
TRYING TO EAT.

04:12.353 --> 04:14.322
- IT'S CLASSIC
END-OF-THE-AFFAIR REMORSE.

04:14.355 --> 04:15.188
- MADE WORSE BY THE FACT THAT

04:15.222 --> 04:16.890
YOU DON'T HAVE ANYONE
TO REPLACE HIM.

04:16.924 --> 04:19.493
- IT'S MY OWN FAULT.

04:19.527 --> 04:22.029
I SHOULDN'T HAVE LET MYSELF BE
INFLUENCED BY OTHER PEOPLE.

04:22.062 --> 04:23.631
- WELL, YOU OBVIOUSLY
HAD YOUR DOUBTS

04:23.664 --> 04:25.566
OR ELSE YOU'D HAVE TOLD US
ALL TO GO FUCK OURSELVES.

04:25.599 --> 04:27.901
- THERE'S PROBABLY
SOME TRUTH TO THAT, MICHAEL.

04:27.935 --> 04:30.070
- DO YOU THINK IT'S TOO LATE?

04:30.103 --> 04:32.373
- YOU KNOW, I ORDERED
MY EGGS WITH BACON...

04:32.406 --> 04:35.509
- OKAY.
- NOT GROUP THERAPY.

04:35.543 --> 04:37.445
- OH.

04:37.478 --> 04:41.949
- IF YOU WANT BEN BACK,
GO FUCKING GET HIM.

04:41.982 --> 04:43.351
- HEY!

04:43.384 --> 04:47.355
YOUR SIDE OF BACON.

04:47.388 --> 04:49.390
OH, WELL.

04:49.423 --> 04:50.824
CAN'T PASTE IT
BACK ON THE PIG.

04:50.858 --> 04:53.594
[laughter]

04:53.627 --> 04:55.963
UH-OH.

04:55.996 --> 04:59.500
THOSE PUPPY DOG EYES
CAN ONLY MEAN ONE THING.

04:59.533 --> 05:01.068
BOY TROUBLE.

05:01.101 --> 05:02.403
- [mouthing silently]
BEN.

05:02.436 --> 05:05.072
- OH.

05:05.105 --> 05:08.075
HONEY.

05:08.108 --> 05:11.679
THE RIGHT GUY'LL COME ALONG.
YOU'LL SEE.

05:11.712 --> 05:13.614
AND WHEN HE DOES,
YOU'LL BE RIGHT THERE

05:13.647 --> 05:15.816
WITH YOUR BIG, WARM HEART

05:15.849 --> 05:17.785
AND THAT FACE
THAT YOU JUST WANNA PINCH

05:17.818 --> 05:19.420
LIKE A PEACH.

05:19.453 --> 05:21.989
MM! LOOK AT THAT.

05:22.022 --> 05:23.891
RIGHT?

05:23.924 --> 05:24.992
DON'T FORGET,

05:25.025 --> 05:27.695
MONDAY NIGHT, ZITI NIGHT.

05:27.728 --> 05:29.963
- GREAT,
SO I CAN BE FAT AND SINGLE.

05:29.997 --> 05:31.732
- [giggles]

05:31.765 --> 05:32.833
- I'M TELLING YOU, BRIAN,

05:32.866 --> 05:34.067
SHE'S DRIVING ME
OUT OF MY MIND.

05:34.101 --> 05:35.102
[glass shatters]

05:35.135 --> 05:37.104
I TOLD YOU TWO TO BEHAVE!

05:37.137 --> 05:38.839
- HE DID IT.

05:38.872 --> 05:39.840
- NO, HE DID.

05:39.873 --> 05:40.974
- FAGGOT.

05:41.008 --> 05:42.376
- HOMO.

05:42.410 --> 05:45.446
- LOOK, SIT DOWN AND SHUT UP.
- HEY!

05:45.479 --> 05:47.448
- OR I'LL MAKE SURE YOUR BALLS
NEVER DROP.

05:47.481 --> 05:49.717
- YOU KNOW,
I DO EVERYTHING FOR HER.

05:49.750 --> 05:51.819
DO YOU THINK
SHE APPRECIATES IT?

05:51.852 --> 05:53.587
DO YOU THINK SHE EVER SAYS,
"THANK YOU"?

05:53.621 --> 05:55.623
ALL SHE DOES IS CRITICIZE.

05:55.656 --> 05:58.726
I MEAN, NOTHING
IS GOOD ENOUGH FOR HER.

05:58.759 --> 06:00.894
- WHY DON'T YOU KILL HER?

06:00.928 --> 06:02.129
NO JURY ON EARTH
WOULD CONVICT YOU.

06:02.162 --> 06:03.864
THEY ALL HAVE MOTHERS
OF THEIR OWN.

06:03.897 --> 06:05.132
- I HAVE A BETTER IDEA.

06:05.165 --> 06:06.834
YOU DEAL WITH HER.

06:06.867 --> 06:07.835
YOU PUT UP WITH HER DEMANDS,

06:07.868 --> 06:09.737
HER DRINKING,

06:09.770 --> 06:11.739
WHICH HAS GOTTEN
A LOT WORSE SINCE DADDY DIED.

06:11.772 --> 06:13.140
- SHE'S CELEBRATING.

06:13.173 --> 06:14.742
- WHY DON'T YOU DRIVE HER
TO THE DOCTOR,

06:14.775 --> 06:17.711
TO CHURCH,
TO GET HER HAIR DONE?

06:17.745 --> 06:19.112
- FUCK THAT SHIT.

06:19.146 --> 06:20.514
[boys snickering]

06:20.548 --> 06:22.416
- SHUT UP.

06:22.450 --> 06:23.717
SHE'S YOUR MOTHER TOO,

06:23.751 --> 06:25.519
AND YOU CAN'T
JUST STICK ME WITH HER.

06:25.553 --> 06:28.422
- IT'S WORKED SO FAR.
- WELL, NOT ANYMORE.

06:28.456 --> 06:29.757
I'VE LOOKED AFTER HER--

06:29.790 --> 06:31.625
WELL, AFTER BOTH OF THEM,
EVER SINCE WE WERE KIDS

06:31.659 --> 06:33.160
WHILE YOU JUST GOT
OFF SCOT-FREE.

06:33.193 --> 06:35.763
NOW EITHER YOU HELP ME OUT,
BRIAN,

06:35.796 --> 06:37.097
OR I SWEAR,

06:37.130 --> 06:38.466
SHE'S YOURS.

06:38.499 --> 06:39.833
ALL YOURS.

06:39.867 --> 06:42.035
[boys squabbling]

06:42.069 --> 06:43.871
COME ON, LET'S GO.
- AW. I DON'T WANNA GO.

06:43.904 --> 06:45.439
- I SAID WE'RE GOING.
LET'S GO.

06:45.473 --> 06:47.207
- AW.
- AW, THIS SUCKS.

06:47.240 --> 06:50.744
[indistinct speech]
[door sliding]

06:56.216 --> 06:58.151
- [sighs]

06:58.185 --> 07:00.988
- [snoring]

07:01.021 --> 07:05.058
- WELL, I'VE DONE COP, COWBOY.
INDIAN CHIEF.

07:05.092 --> 07:07.795
AFTER THIS, I GUESS I'VE DONE
THE VILLAGE PEOPLE.

07:07.828 --> 07:09.663
- [snores]

07:09.697 --> 07:10.731
- TED?

07:10.764 --> 07:13.166
- [snorts]
- HEY.

07:13.200 --> 07:15.035
- HUH?
- POOR BABY.

07:15.068 --> 07:17.805
YOU REALLY ARE EXHAUSTED.

07:19.039 --> 07:21.575
- INVOICES. PAYROLL.

07:21.609 --> 07:23.877
ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE.

07:23.911 --> 07:27.848
IT'S LIKE WERTSHAFTER'S
TIMES A THOUSAND.

07:27.881 --> 07:32.152
AND I'M SUPPOSED TO MEET THOR
THE IMPALER TONIGHT.

07:32.185 --> 07:34.054
OH, WHAT'S THE POINT?

07:34.087 --> 07:35.823
I'M TOO TIRED
TO EVEN GET IT UP.

07:35.856 --> 07:36.957
- HONEY,

07:36.990 --> 07:39.760
YOU ARE IN THE BIZ.

07:39.793 --> 07:41.929
A HARD DICK

07:41.962 --> 07:46.233
IS AT YOUR FINGERTIPS.

07:46.266 --> 07:48.035
- "VIAGRA"?

07:49.837 --> 07:50.938
I DON'T KNOW.

07:50.971 --> 07:52.573
I HAVEN'T EXACTLY HAD
A WINNING SCORE

07:52.606 --> 07:53.574
WHEN IT COMES TO DRUGS.

07:53.607 --> 07:55.108
- I UNDERSTAND YOUR TREPIDATION.

07:55.142 --> 07:56.910
AND NORMALLY
I'D AGREE WITH YOU,

07:56.944 --> 08:00.981
BUT, UH, BUT THIS STUFF
IS MADE FOR OCTOGENARIANS.

08:01.014 --> 08:03.150
IF THEY CAN FUCK LIKE
SOMEONE WHO'S 30,

08:03.183 --> 08:06.720
EVEN YOU SHOULD BE ABLE
TO FUCK LIKE SOMEONE WHO'S 80.

08:06.754 --> 08:07.921
- YOU EVER TRIED IT?

08:07.955 --> 08:10.791
- ONLY WHEN I OPERATE
HEAVY EQUIPMENT.

08:10.824 --> 08:12.292
- AND?

08:12.325 --> 08:14.728
- LASTS FOR A FEW HOURS, TOPS.

08:14.762 --> 08:16.664
BUT LONG ENOUGH
TO HAVE A NIGHT

08:16.697 --> 08:19.099
YOU'LL NEVER FORGET.

08:28.108 --> 08:30.644
- BEN.

08:30.678 --> 08:32.179
- HEY, MICHAEL.

08:32.212 --> 08:34.915
- WHAT A COINCIDENCE,
MY RUNNING INTO YOU.

08:34.948 --> 08:37.050
- UH, NOT REALLY.
I LIVE HERE.

08:40.854 --> 08:43.290
WELL, IT WAS NICE
SEEING YOU.

08:45.926 --> 08:48.629
- THE TRUTH IS, I'VE BEEN
WALKING UP AND DOWN THE BLOCK

08:48.662 --> 08:50.998
FOR TWO HOURS WAITING FOR YOU.

08:53.867 --> 08:55.936
- WOULD YOU LIKE TO COME UP?

08:55.969 --> 08:58.972
CAN I GET YOU SOMETHING
TO DRINK?

08:59.006 --> 09:01.642
- NO. THANKS.

09:01.675 --> 09:05.012
- OH, A FRIEND OF MINE
GAVE ME THAT.

09:05.045 --> 09:07.715
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO RUB
ITS BELLY FOR LUCK.

09:07.748 --> 09:09.717
- DOES IT WORK?

09:09.750 --> 09:12.252
- CAN'T HURT.

09:12.285 --> 09:15.222
- [quietly] COME THROUGH,
BUDDHA, OL' BUDDY.

09:22.362 --> 09:24.331
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT YOU.

09:24.364 --> 09:27.000
A LOT.

09:27.034 --> 09:29.069
- I'VE THOUGHT ABOUT YOU TOO.

09:29.102 --> 09:31.939
- YEAH?

09:31.972 --> 09:34.107
I THINK
I MAY HAVE OVERREACTED.

09:34.141 --> 09:39.079
YOU KNOW,
TO YOU BEING POSITIVE.

09:39.112 --> 09:41.014
- HMM.

09:41.048 --> 09:42.716
- I LISTENED TO
A LOT OF PEOPLE

09:42.750 --> 09:45.118
WHEN I SHOULD HAVE LISTENED
TO MYSELF.

09:45.152 --> 09:48.221
ANYWAY...

09:48.255 --> 09:52.092
I'D LIKE TO START AGAIN.

09:52.125 --> 09:54.227
THAT IS,
IF YOU'RE NOT SEEING ANYONE.

09:54.261 --> 09:56.964
YOU'RE NOT SEEING ANYONE,
ARE YOU?

09:56.997 --> 09:59.366
- NO.

09:59.399 --> 10:02.135
- WELL, GOOD THEN...

10:02.169 --> 10:03.971
WE CAN PICK UP
WHERE WE LEFT OFF.

10:04.004 --> 10:06.940
- [chuckles]

10:06.974 --> 10:09.843
LOOK, UH, I APPRECIATE
YOUR COMING TO SEE ME

10:09.877 --> 10:11.111
AND EVERYTHING YOU SAID

10:11.144 --> 10:16.116
THAT THIS TIME
IT WOULD BE DIFFERENT.

10:16.149 --> 10:18.952
BUT I CAN'T TAKE THAT CHANCE.

10:18.986 --> 10:19.753
I NEED TO KNOW THAT

10:19.787 --> 10:21.822
IF I ALLOW MYSELF
TO LOVE SOMEONE,

10:21.855 --> 10:24.391
THAT THEY'RE NOT GONNA
BAIL ON ME.

10:24.424 --> 10:26.126
NO MATTER WHAT THEIR FRIENDS
OR THEIR MOTHER SAY,

10:26.159 --> 10:29.963
I NEED TO KNOW
THEY'LL BE THERE.

10:31.732 --> 10:33.667
SO I'M SORRY.

10:33.701 --> 10:38.038
BUT IT TAKES MORE
THAN A KISS.

10:38.071 --> 10:39.673
- OH.

10:39.707 --> 10:42.275
- IT'S BEEN AN HOUR
SINCE I TOOK IT.

10:42.309 --> 10:44.111
- WELL, THERE ARE
NO HARD OR FIRM RULES

10:44.144 --> 10:45.746
WHEN IT COMES
TO THESE THINGS.

10:45.779 --> 10:47.047
IT'LL HAPPEN WHEN IT HAPPENS.

10:47.080 --> 10:48.115
- WELL, I DON'T WANT
ANYTHING TO HAPPEN

10:48.148 --> 10:49.783
TILL THOR ARRIVES.
[phone beeps]

10:49.817 --> 10:51.351
HOLD ON.
[phone beeps]

10:51.384 --> 10:52.419
HELLO?

10:52.452 --> 10:54.454
- IT'S ME. THOR.

10:54.487 --> 10:56.690
- HEY.

10:56.724 --> 10:58.826
SO, UH--
[dog yaps]

10:58.859 --> 11:00.928
WHEN ARE YOU COMING OVER?

11:00.961 --> 11:02.429
- I CAN'T.
MY DOG'S THROWING UP.

11:02.462 --> 11:03.997
I-I GOTTA TAKE HER
TO THE HOSPITAL.

11:04.031 --> 11:05.432
[dog gagging]

11:05.465 --> 11:08.836
CHRIST, LULU!

11:08.869 --> 11:10.270
SHE DID IT AGAIN.

11:10.303 --> 11:11.371
I GOTTA GO.

11:11.404 --> 11:14.842
- OKAY.

11:14.875 --> 11:16.777
- TED?
- THAT WAS THOR.

11:16.810 --> 11:18.846
LULU'S THROWING UP.

11:18.879 --> 11:20.280
- WHO'S LULU?

11:20.313 --> 11:22.449
- OH, GOD.

11:22.482 --> 11:23.751
I'M GETTING HARD.

11:23.784 --> 11:25.953
- OH, THERE, YOU SEE?
IT'S WORKING.

11:25.986 --> 11:28.355
OH, IT'S WORKING.

11:28.388 --> 11:30.891
- YEAH, WHOO-HOO.
WHAT DO I DO NOW?

11:30.924 --> 11:32.860
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"WHAT DO YOU DO NOW?"

11:32.893 --> 11:34.294
YOU NEED A MANUAL?

11:34.327 --> 11:35.963
HONEY, I'VE SEEN YOU
IN ACTION.

11:35.996 --> 11:38.165
WE'VE ALL SEEN YOU
IN ACTION.

11:38.198 --> 11:40.200
I'M SURE YOU'LL COME UP
WITH SOMETHING.

11:40.233 --> 11:42.202
- THANKS.
[phone beeps]

11:43.837 --> 11:45.873
- MM.

11:45.906 --> 11:47.307
- WOW.

11:47.340 --> 11:49.342
[groans]

11:51.478 --> 11:53.914
- IT'S A LITTLE EARLY
FOR THAT, ISN'T IT?

11:53.947 --> 11:56.149
- JUST SOMETHING
TO CALM MY NERVES.

11:56.183 --> 11:59.853
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
I SAW YOU?

11:59.887 --> 12:01.288
- CHRISTMAS.

12:01.321 --> 12:05.492
- YOU STAYED FOR AN HOUR.
BROUGHT ME FLOWERS.

12:05.525 --> 12:07.761
SAME ONES.

12:09.963 --> 12:11.899
MM.

12:11.932 --> 12:14.968
WE BETTER GO,
WE DON'T WANT TO BE LATE.

12:15.002 --> 12:17.871
- FOR WHAT?
- CHURCH.

12:17.905 --> 12:19.339
- CHURCH?

12:19.372 --> 12:22.542
- CLAIRE SAID YOU'D TAKE ME.

12:22.575 --> 12:26.046
- I NEVER SAID THAT.

12:28.982 --> 12:29.917
THAT BITCH.

12:29.950 --> 12:35.322
- BRIAN, DO YOU HAVE TO USE
SUCH LANGUAGE?

12:35.355 --> 12:37.457
- WE ALWAYS WENT
TO THE 8:00 SERVICE.

12:37.490 --> 12:39.893
- WELL, I'VE SWITCHED
TO THE NOON ONE.

12:39.927 --> 12:42.062
IT'S MORE TRADITIONAL.

12:42.095 --> 12:47.067
AND WE HAVE
THIS WONDERFUL NEW MINISTER.

12:51.104 --> 12:52.339
ARE YOU COMING?

12:52.372 --> 12:55.809
- HELL NO.

12:55.843 --> 12:58.879
- FINE.

12:58.912 --> 13:03.250
I'LL GO MYSELF.

13:03.283 --> 13:08.021
- YOU CAN'T GO LIKE THAT.

13:08.055 --> 13:11.892
- DARLING, I'VE MANAGED
QUITE WELL ON MY OWN

13:11.925 --> 13:16.563
WITHOUT YOU,
WITHOUT ANYONE MY ENTIRE LIFE.

13:16.596 --> 13:18.165
TRULY, I CAN DO IT.

13:18.198 --> 13:20.033
I DON'T NEED YOU.

13:20.067 --> 13:23.036
[rap music]

13:23.070 --> 13:31.011
*

13:31.979 --> 13:36.950
[overlapping shouting]

13:40.888 --> 13:42.289
- YEAH!

13:42.322 --> 13:45.058
- WOW.
PRETTY COOL.

13:45.092 --> 13:48.028
THE NFL SHOULD SIGN YOU UP.

13:48.061 --> 13:49.196
- UH, THAT'S FOOTBALL.

13:49.229 --> 13:51.598
- RIGHT, RIGHT.
I MEANT--I MEANT THE NBL.

13:51.631 --> 13:55.002
- THERE IS NO NBL.

13:55.035 --> 13:57.204
- OKAY, I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT BASKETBALL.

13:57.237 --> 13:58.939
BUT IN CASE
YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED, I'M QUEER.

13:58.972 --> 14:00.440
- WELL, I LOVE BASKETBALL.

14:00.473 --> 14:02.075
IN CASE YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED,
I'M QUEER TOO.

14:02.109 --> 14:03.310
- OH, I'VE NOTICED.

14:03.343 --> 14:04.511
- WHAT'S UP, KING,
WHAT'S UP?

14:04.544 --> 14:06.246
D'YOU WANT THE BALL?
WHAT'S UP?

14:06.279 --> 14:08.348
[shouting indistinctly]

14:08.381 --> 14:16.323
*

14:19.026 --> 14:22.295
- YEAH!
- WHOO! [laughs]

14:22.329 --> 14:25.165
- YO, GUYS, I GOTTA GO.

14:25.198 --> 14:27.534
- I'LL COVER.

14:27.567 --> 14:29.536
OOF.

14:32.705 --> 14:35.375
ALL RIGHT. LET'S PLAY BALL.

14:35.408 --> 14:37.277
- I'LL COVER MIGHTY MOUSE.

14:37.310 --> 14:38.411
- ALL RIGHT, WAIT.
COME ON.

14:38.445 --> 14:39.412
THESE GUYS
ARE GONNA TROUNCE YOU.

14:39.446 --> 14:40.213
GIVE ME THE BALL.
- NO.

14:40.247 --> 14:42.149
- I SAID GIVE ME THE BALL,
MICHAEL.

14:42.182 --> 14:44.451
- NOT UNTIL YOU AGREE TO GO
OUT WITH ME. TONIGHT.

14:44.484 --> 14:46.954
- PARDON ME?
THE BALL.

14:46.987 --> 14:49.389
- KEEP YOUR SHORTS ON, GODZILLA.
- HUH?

14:49.422 --> 14:51.024
- I'M NOT HANDING OVER
THE BALL

14:51.058 --> 14:54.227
UNTIL HE AGREES TO GO OUT
WITH ME ON A DATE.

14:54.261 --> 14:55.929
- ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

14:55.963 --> 14:58.398
- YOU MET MY MOTHER.
DO YOU REALLY NEED TO ASK THAT?

14:58.431 --> 15:00.400
HUH?

15:03.403 --> 15:05.005
- I SUGGEST YOU SAY YES,

15:05.038 --> 15:07.007
'CAUSE IF HE'S LIKE THE BITCH
I GOT AT HOME,

15:07.040 --> 15:10.010
WE'RE GONNA BE STANDING HERE
ALL DAY.

15:10.043 --> 15:12.045
[overlapping chatter]

15:12.079 --> 15:17.617
*

15:17.650 --> 15:22.589
[church bells toll]

15:24.124 --> 15:27.127
[organ music]

15:27.160 --> 15:29.162
*

15:29.196 --> 15:32.499
- HI.

15:32.532 --> 15:34.167
- JESUS.

15:34.201 --> 15:35.702
I TOLD HIM TO LAY OFF
THE SLIM-FAST.

15:35.735 --> 15:38.205
- SHH.
BEHAVE YOURSELF.

15:38.238 --> 15:40.073
WHEN WERE YOU LAST IN CHURCH?

15:42.642 --> 15:44.477
- IT'S BEEN A WHILE.

15:47.347 --> 15:50.383
- WELL, WHENEVER I COME HERE...

15:50.417 --> 15:53.520
I FEEL A SENSE OF CALM,

15:53.553 --> 15:58.325
OF INNER PEACE
KNOWING THAT I'M WATCHED OVER.

15:58.358 --> 15:59.526
PROTECTED.

15:59.559 --> 16:02.095
SAFE.

16:02.129 --> 16:04.097
- YEAH, WELL, A GOOD SECURITY
SYSTEM WOULD DO THE SAME JOB

16:04.131 --> 16:05.198
AND IN THE LONG RUN
BE A LOT CHEAPER

16:05.232 --> 16:06.466
THAN ALL THOSE DEPOSITS
YOU'VE DROPPED

16:06.499 --> 16:09.069
IN THE OFFERING PLATE
OVER THE YEARS.

16:09.102 --> 16:12.072
- WAIT TILL YOU SEE
OUR NEW MINISTER.

16:12.105 --> 16:14.641
I CAN'T TELL YOU WHAT
A COMFORT HE'S BEEN TO ME

16:14.674 --> 16:17.110
SINCE YOUR FATHER DIED.

16:17.144 --> 16:20.113
HE CALLS, HE VISITS.

16:20.147 --> 16:23.050
HE MAKES SURE I'M ALL RIGHT.

16:23.083 --> 16:26.586
OH, HE'S BEEN...LIKE A SON.

16:26.619 --> 16:28.088
- WELL, FOR HIS SAKE,

16:28.121 --> 16:30.257
I SURE HOPE YOU DON'T
TREAT HIM LIKE ONE.

16:30.290 --> 16:32.459
- HERE HE IS.

16:40.533 --> 16:42.635
- THE GRACE OF OUR LORD,
JESUS CHRIST,

16:42.669 --> 16:43.503
THE LOVE OF GOD

16:43.536 --> 16:46.806
AND THE COMMUNION
OF THE HOLY SPIRIT

16:46.839 --> 16:48.375
BE WITH YOU ALL.

16:48.408 --> 16:51.344
- AND WITH YOU.

16:54.747 --> 16:56.116
- [moans]

16:58.651 --> 17:00.253
GOOD AFTERNOON, EVERYONE,

17:00.287 --> 17:03.790
AND, UH, WELCOME.

17:03.823 --> 17:05.325
- [snickers]
- AS WE BEGIN OUR WORSHIP...

17:05.358 --> 17:06.326
- SHH.
- SORRY.

17:06.359 --> 17:07.827
- LET US PRAY.

17:07.860 --> 17:11.631
[birds chirping]

17:11.664 --> 17:14.634
[sweeping orchestration]

17:14.667 --> 17:22.609
*

17:28.181 --> 17:29.816
- AAH!

17:29.849 --> 17:32.552
[church bells toll]

17:32.585 --> 17:36.389
- WASN'T HE WONDERFUL?

17:36.423 --> 17:37.857
I WANT YOU TO COME
AND SAY HELLO.

17:37.890 --> 17:38.991
I'VE TOLD HIM ALL ABOUT YOU.

17:39.025 --> 17:42.162
I TOLD HIM HOW SUCCESSFUL
AND GOOD-LOOKING YOU ARE.

17:42.195 --> 17:43.630
HE'S JUST DYING TO MEET YOU.

17:43.663 --> 17:45.798
- I'LL BET.
- BYE.

17:45.832 --> 17:47.567
- REVEREND TOM.
- JOAN.

17:47.600 --> 17:48.701
- [laughs]

17:48.735 --> 17:50.637
- YOU NEVER MISS
A SINGLE SUNDAY.

17:50.670 --> 17:52.172
- NOT FOR THE WORLD.

17:52.205 --> 17:54.541
YOU'LL NEVER GUESS
WHO'S WITH ME--MY SON.

17:54.574 --> 17:55.708
- THAT'S WONDERFUL.

17:55.742 --> 17:56.876
- LET ME INTRODUCE YOU.

17:56.909 --> 17:58.578
BRIAN.

17:58.611 --> 18:01.581
THIS IS
REVEREND TOM BUTTERFIELD.

18:01.614 --> 18:04.584
- REVEREND BUTTERFIELD.

18:04.617 --> 18:08.455
MY MOTHER'S TOLD ME
SO MUCH ABOUT YOU.

18:08.488 --> 18:11.391
IT'S UNCANNY.
I FEEL AS IF WE'VE ALREADY MET.

18:11.424 --> 18:13.460
- OH, EXCUSE ME.

18:13.493 --> 18:14.894
RUTH!

18:14.927 --> 18:15.895
- HELLO, JOAN.

18:15.928 --> 18:17.297
- HI.
- HOW ARE YOU DOING?

18:17.330 --> 18:18.731
- GREAT SERVICE.

18:18.765 --> 18:19.866
- I'M GLAD YOU ENJOYED IT.

18:19.899 --> 18:22.369
- I MEANT AT THE BATHS.
- LOOK, LOOK--

18:22.402 --> 18:23.703
- GOOD SERMON, REVEREND TOM.

18:23.736 --> 18:27.374
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH
FOR COMING.

18:27.407 --> 18:28.808
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

18:28.841 --> 18:30.343
- ME EITHER.
[chuckles]

18:30.377 --> 18:32.512
AND I'VE FUCKED PRACTICALLY
EVERYBODY IN THIS BURGH.

18:32.545 --> 18:34.747
BUT THIS...
[laughs]

18:34.781 --> 18:36.416
THIS IS A FIRST.

18:36.449 --> 18:37.617
- I WOULD APPRECIATE IT

18:37.650 --> 18:40.220
IF YOU'D KEEP THIS
BETWEEN THE TWO OF US.

18:40.253 --> 18:41.688
- YOU THINK I'M GONNA TELL
MY MOM?

18:41.721 --> 18:44.824
- BYE-BYE.
- SHE DOESN'T EVEN KNOW I'M GAY.

18:44.857 --> 18:46.359
AND I HAVEN'T TALKED
TO YOUR BOSS FOR YEARS,

18:46.393 --> 18:47.760
SO DON'T WORRY, REV.

18:47.794 --> 18:52.131
YOUR SECRET'S SAFE WITH ME.

18:53.966 --> 18:56.869
- SO YOU FUCKED
YOUR MOTHER'S MINISTER?

18:56.903 --> 18:58.638
- MM-HMM.
- YOU SHOULD'VE SEEN IT.

18:58.671 --> 18:59.806
IT WAS TOTALLY HOT.

18:59.839 --> 19:01.841
- ISN'T HE TAKING QUITE
A CHANCE?

19:01.874 --> 19:04.244
- THE AVERAGE AGE
OF HIS PARISH IS 102.

19:04.277 --> 19:06.446
I DOUBT THEY'RE HANGING OUT
AT THE BATHS.

19:06.479 --> 19:08.748
- I ONCE WANTED
TO BE A PRIEST.

19:08.781 --> 19:11.318
BUT THEN I THOUGHT,
HOW UNNATURAL,

19:11.351 --> 19:14.487
LIVING YOUR LIFE CLOISTERED
AWAY IN A WORLD FULL OF MEN.

19:14.521 --> 19:17.657
[cell phone beeps]
HMM? MM.

19:17.690 --> 19:19.892
IT'S ME.
[cell phone beeps]

19:19.926 --> 19:20.893
HELLO?

19:20.927 --> 19:22.329
- [whispers]
IT'S ME.

19:22.362 --> 19:23.730
- TEDDY?
- SHH!

19:23.763 --> 19:25.798
- WHERE ARE YOU?

19:25.832 --> 19:27.734
- ON MEL AND LINDSAY'S
FRONT PORCH.

19:27.767 --> 19:29.602
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING ON
THE FRONT PORCH, HONEY?

19:29.636 --> 19:30.603
WHY DON'T YOU COME IN?

19:30.637 --> 19:32.539
- BECAUSE I DON'T WANT
THE OTHERS TO SEE ME.

19:32.572 --> 19:34.707
I'VE GOT TO TALK TO YOU.

19:34.741 --> 19:36.609
SO JUST SLIP OUTSIDE

19:36.643 --> 19:38.345
LIKE YOU'RE GONNA
CHECK ON THE WEATHER.

19:38.378 --> 19:41.814
BUT PROMISE, PROMISE,
PROMISE ME

19:41.848 --> 19:45.618
YOU'LL COME ALONE.

19:48.455 --> 19:49.422
- COME HAVE SOME BRUNCH.

19:49.456 --> 19:50.957
- UH, NO. NO.
NO THANK YOU.

19:50.990 --> 19:53.593
UH, I JUST, UH,
I NEED TO TALK WITH EMMETT

19:53.626 --> 19:56.463
AND, UH,
THEN I'LL BE ON MY WAY.

19:56.496 --> 19:58.465
- OKAY.

19:58.498 --> 20:00.400
- [whispers]
I STILL HAVE AN ERECTION.

20:00.433 --> 20:02.001
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN
YOU STILL HAVE AN ERECTION?

20:02.034 --> 20:05.438
[laughter]

20:05.472 --> 20:08.007
- THANK YOU, CNN.

20:08.040 --> 20:11.544
I TOOK VIAGRA LAST NIGHT.

20:11.578 --> 20:13.846
IT'S BEEN 18 HOURS,
AND IT WON'T GO DOWN.

20:13.880 --> 20:15.248
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

20:15.282 --> 20:16.716
- HAVE YOU TRIED SOAKING IT?

20:16.749 --> 20:17.917
- HOW ABOUT A COLD SHOWER?

20:17.950 --> 20:18.918
- HOW ABOUT SCARING IT?

20:18.951 --> 20:19.986
- THAT'S HICCUPS.

20:20.019 --> 20:21.354
- BOO!

20:21.388 --> 20:22.589
- OKAY, THANK YOU
ALL FOR CARING.

20:22.622 --> 20:25.024
- WHAT ABOUT SOMETHING THAT
WOULD ABSOLUTELY TURN YOU OFF?

20:25.057 --> 20:26.359
- THAT'S A GREAT IDEA.

20:26.393 --> 20:27.827
WHY DON'T YOU TWO
SHOW HIM YOUR TITS?

20:27.860 --> 20:28.828
women: BRIAN.

20:28.861 --> 20:31.498
- YOU SAID THIS WOULD LAST
A FEW HOURS, TOPS.

20:31.531 --> 20:32.765
- GO FIGURE.

20:32.799 --> 20:34.534
- MAYBE YOU SHOULD TAKE SOME.

20:34.567 --> 20:36.603
OUR SEX LIFE ISN'T
WHAT IT USED TO BE.

20:36.636 --> 20:37.637
- [scoffs]

20:37.670 --> 20:40.540
- WELL, WE'RE DOWN TO LIKE,
FOUR TIMES A DAY.

20:40.573 --> 20:42.375
- LOOK,
I'VE GOTTA DO SOMETHING.

20:42.409 --> 20:45.378
- OKAY. OKAY. COME ON.

20:45.412 --> 20:47.580
- WELL, JUST TRY
AND MAKE IT TILL NEXT MONDAY.

20:47.614 --> 20:48.648
- WHAT'S NEXT MONDAY?

20:48.681 --> 20:49.649
- IT'S FLAG DAY. WHOO!

20:49.682 --> 20:51.751
[laughter]

20:53.753 --> 20:55.488
- BYE.

20:55.522 --> 20:56.789
- [grunting]

20:56.823 --> 20:58.625
- I CAN'T BELIEVE...

20:58.658 --> 21:01.994
YOU'RE FUCKING ME...

21:02.028 --> 21:06.399
AGAIN.

21:06.433 --> 21:08.935
- IT WAS YOUR IDEA...

21:08.968 --> 21:11.704
TO STEAL...

21:11.738 --> 21:13.673
TED'S...

21:13.706 --> 21:15.342
VIAGRA.

21:15.375 --> 21:18.778
[grunts]

21:18.811 --> 21:21.948
[both panting]
[knock on door]

21:25.117 --> 21:28.755
[knock on door]

21:31.758 --> 21:35.528
- ARE YOU GONNA ANSWER?

21:35.562 --> 21:38.398
- THEY'LL GO AWAY.

21:38.431 --> 21:41.434
[groans]
[knock on door]

21:48.808 --> 21:50.577
MOM.

21:50.610 --> 21:53.012
- I'M SORRY,
AM I DISTURBING YOU?

21:53.045 --> 21:56.048
I-I WAS GOING TO LEAVE THIS
HERE BY THE DOOR WITH A NOTE,

21:56.082 --> 21:58.351
BUT THEN I THOUGHT
AS LONG AS I'M HERE...

21:58.385 --> 22:00.420
- I MIGHT AS WELL BANG
ON HIS DOOR A MILLION TIMES

22:00.453 --> 22:02.555
AND DRIVE HIM NUTS
UNTIL HE ANSWERS.

22:02.589 --> 22:04.424
- IT'S YOUR FAVORITE--

22:04.457 --> 22:08.861
CHOCOLATE-CHOCOLATE CHIP.

22:14.000 --> 22:17.937
IT'S JUST MY WAY
OF SAYING THANK YOU

22:17.970 --> 22:20.907
FOR GOING WITH ME TO CHURCH.

22:20.940 --> 22:25.545
I CAN'T TELL YOU
HOW MUCH IT MEANT.

22:25.578 --> 22:30.016
- LE--LET'S DO IT AGAIN.
SOON.

22:30.049 --> 22:33.786
- I KNOW YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

22:33.820 --> 22:38.891
I PROBABLY WON'T SEE YOU AGAIN
FOR ANOTHER SIX MONTHS.

22:38.925 --> 22:41.127
IF YOU HAD ANY IDEA
HOW LONELY IT GETS

22:41.160 --> 22:43.930
NOW THAT YOUR FATHER
IS GONE...

22:43.963 --> 22:49.702
I'M IN THAT HOUSE
NIGHT AND DAY BY MYSELF.

22:49.736 --> 22:54.841
THE PHONE NEVER RINGS.

22:59.178 --> 23:04.517
IF ONLY...WE COULD BE CLOSE.

23:04.551 --> 23:05.818
THE WAY WE ONCE WERE.

23:05.852 --> 23:07.720
- BRIAN?

23:07.754 --> 23:10.557
ARE YOU COMING BACK?

23:10.590 --> 23:13.860
- I DIDN'T KNOW THERE
WAS SOMEONE ELSE HERE.

23:20.199 --> 23:21.768
- JUSTIN,
THIS IS...

23:21.801 --> 23:24.771
MY MOTHER.

23:26.238 --> 23:30.777
MOM, THIS IS JUSTIN.

23:30.810 --> 23:33.746
- HI.

23:37.016 --> 23:38.951
[button rings]

23:40.219 --> 23:41.521
- MOM.

23:41.554 --> 23:44.624
[elevator motor humming]

23:48.628 --> 23:50.530
WHAT?

23:50.563 --> 23:53.800
YOU'RE NOT GONNA TALK TO ME?

23:55.602 --> 23:58.505
- THANK GOD
YOUR FATHER DIDN'T KNOW.

23:58.538 --> 23:59.672
- HE DID.

24:03.510 --> 24:07.446
I TOLD HIM BEFORE HE DIED.

24:12.619 --> 24:15.588
- WHAT ABOUT YOUR SISTER?

24:22.729 --> 24:25.565
SO YOU TOLD EVERYONE BUT ME.

24:29.569 --> 24:32.104
I HOPE YOU KNOW IT'S A SIN.

24:32.138 --> 24:36.075
- THAT I FUCK GUYS
OR THAT I DIDN'T TELL YOU?

24:42.882 --> 24:45.251
- YOU CAN MAKE
ALL THE JOKES YOU WANT.

24:45.284 --> 24:47.987
THE BIBLE MAKES IT CLEAR.

24:48.020 --> 24:49.221
YOU'RE GOING TO HELL.

24:49.255 --> 24:51.490
[elevator door closes]

25:04.771 --> 25:09.642
- MM-HMM.

25:09.676 --> 25:10.810
MM, MM-HMM.

25:10.843 --> 25:13.312
- WELL, WHAT IS IT, DOCTOR?

25:13.345 --> 25:16.549
- WELL, THAT'S QUITE
A BONER YOU'VE GOT THERE.

25:16.583 --> 25:17.917
- NOTHING LIKE
THE EXPERT DIAGNOSIS OF

25:17.950 --> 25:19.652
A TRAINED MEDICAL PROFESSIONAL.

25:19.686 --> 25:21.287
- SHUSH.

25:21.320 --> 25:24.824
- BUT DOCTOR,
WHY WON'T IT GO DOWN?

25:24.857 --> 25:26.025
- IT'S A PRIAPISM--

25:26.058 --> 25:27.627
A BLOOD CLOT TO THE PENIS.

25:27.660 --> 25:28.628
- OH, MY GOD.

25:28.661 --> 25:30.296
- WELL, IT'S BETTER

25:30.329 --> 25:32.031
THAN A BLOOD CLOT
TO THE BRAIN.

25:32.064 --> 25:36.869
- UNLESS YOU THINK
WITH YOUR DICK.

25:36.903 --> 25:38.905
- WELL, THIS IS
EXTREMELY UNUSUAL.

25:38.938 --> 25:41.874
IT'S ONE
FOR THE MEDICAL JOURNALS.

25:41.908 --> 25:43.910
- OR THE GUINNESS BOOK
OF WORLD RECORDS.

25:43.943 --> 25:47.146
- SHUT UP.

25:47.179 --> 25:49.281
SO WHAT DO YOU RECOMMEND?

25:49.315 --> 25:52.619
- ARE YOU IN ANY PAIN?

25:52.652 --> 25:55.054
WELL,
TRY TAKING A DECONGESTANT.

25:55.087 --> 25:57.056
- A DECONGESTANT?

25:57.089 --> 25:58.625
I HAVE A PENIS IN A STATE

25:58.658 --> 25:59.859
OF PERMANENT FIRST STAGE ALERT,

25:59.892 --> 26:00.860
NOT A STUFFED-UP NOSE.

26:00.893 --> 26:01.961
ISN'T THERE ANYTHING

26:01.994 --> 26:03.195
MORE CUTTING-EDGE
YOU CAN DO?

26:03.229 --> 26:04.831
- WELL, ACTUALLY THERE IS.

26:04.864 --> 26:05.932
WE COULD INSERT
TWO WIDE NEEDLES

26:05.965 --> 26:09.201
UP THE SHAFT
AND DRAIN THE BLOOD.

26:11.237 --> 26:14.306
- YOU KNOW, DECONGESTANTS HAVE
BEEN VERY EFFECTIVE FOR ME.

26:14.340 --> 26:18.077
- BUT, UH,
WHEN WILL IT GO DOWN, DOCTOR?

26:18.110 --> 26:20.813
A-A WEEK? MONTH?

26:20.847 --> 26:21.814
A YEAR?

26:21.848 --> 26:22.815
- HMM.

26:22.849 --> 26:24.350
HARD TO SAY.

26:24.383 --> 26:26.686
SORRY.

26:26.719 --> 26:29.321
[playing Hot Stuff]

26:29.355 --> 26:30.757
- * GOTTA HAVE
SOME HOT STUFF *

26:30.790 --> 26:33.626
* GOTTA HAVE
SOME LOVE TONIGHT *

26:33.660 --> 26:35.294
[sirens wail]

26:35.327 --> 26:38.364
* I NEED HOT STUFF

