26:41.868 --> 26:43.135
- GOD, I NEED A STIFF ONE.

26:43.169 --> 26:44.336
- [snickers]

26:44.370 --> 26:46.005
- THE OTHER KIND.

26:46.038 --> 26:47.807
- QUIT WORRYING.
YOU HEARD WHAT THE DOCTOR SAID.

26:47.840 --> 26:48.808
IT'LL GO DOWN.

26:48.841 --> 26:49.976
- YEAH, MINE DID.

26:50.009 --> 26:51.377
- YEAH, THANKS TO YOUR MOM.

26:51.410 --> 26:53.813
SHE CAN MAKE ANYONE LOSE
THEIR HARD-ON.

26:53.846 --> 26:54.981
- CAN I GET HER NUMBER?

26:55.014 --> 26:56.148
- SHE JUST NEEDS A LITTLE TIME

26:56.182 --> 26:57.216
TO GET USED TO IT.

26:57.249 --> 27:00.352
- WHAT? THAT HER BABY BOY
SUCKS HOT, HARD COCK?

27:00.386 --> 27:01.721
- AND LOVES IT.

27:01.754 --> 27:02.989
- YEAH,
SHE'S PROBABLY PRAYING

27:03.022 --> 27:04.657
FOR MY SOUL AS WE SPEAK

27:04.691 --> 27:05.992
WITH REVEREND BUTTFUCK.

27:06.025 --> 27:07.660
- WHAT A JOKE.

27:07.694 --> 27:09.896
- WELL, HE'S THE ONE
SHE BELIEVES IN.

27:09.929 --> 27:12.031
THE ONE SHE TRUSTS.

27:12.064 --> 27:15.334
THE ONE WHO'S BEEN LIKE
A SON TO HER.

27:15.367 --> 27:17.036
IF SHE ONLY KNEW.

27:17.069 --> 27:18.705
- WELL, DON'T WORRY.

27:18.738 --> 27:21.841
GOD STILL LOVES YOU,
NO MATTER WHAT.

27:21.874 --> 27:24.844
- YEAH, LIKE I GIVE A SHIT
WHAT GOD THINKS ABOUT ME.

27:24.877 --> 27:27.146
HE'D BETTER BE WORRIED
WHAT I THINK ABOUT HIM.

27:27.179 --> 27:28.380
- HOW DO YOU FIGURE THAT?

27:28.414 --> 27:30.182
- WELL, IN ALL THIS COLD,
DEAD UNIVERSE

27:30.216 --> 27:32.218
WE'RE THE ONLY ONES
THAT KNOW HE EXISTS.

27:32.251 --> 27:34.821
WITHOUT US, HE'S NOTHING.

27:34.854 --> 27:40.426
[indistinct chatter]

27:40.459 --> 27:42.161
- OH.

27:42.194 --> 27:44.897
[feedback from mic]

27:44.931 --> 27:48.735
YOU CAME.
- I SAID I WOULD, DIDN'T I?

27:48.768 --> 27:50.202
- I'M OVER HERE WITH THE GUYS.

27:50.236 --> 27:52.471
- WHOA.
- * HOT, HOT, HOT, HOT

27:52.504 --> 27:54.106
- I THOUGHT THIS WAS
ABOUT YOU AND ME.

27:54.140 --> 27:56.743
- IT IS. COME ON.

27:56.776 --> 27:58.410
- WHOO-HOO.

27:58.444 --> 28:02.749
- * HOT, HOT, HOT,
HOT STUFF *

28:02.782 --> 28:04.784
- HEY, GUYS, LOOK WHO'S HERE.
- HI, GUYS.

28:04.817 --> 28:06.919
- HEY, BEN.
