- SO DID YOU GUYS
JUST HAPPEN TO

28:13.125 --> 28:14.927
RUN INTO EACH OTHER?

28:14.961 --> 28:16.228
- ACTUALLY--
- UH, NO.

28:16.262 --> 28:20.733
I INVITED HIM.
HE'S MY DATE.

28:20.767 --> 28:22.268
- WELL, I THOUGHT YOU TWO--

28:22.301 --> 28:24.737
- WE DID,
BUT I'M HOPING

28:24.771 --> 28:26.138
WE CAN GET BACK
TOGETHER AGAIN.

28:26.172 --> 28:29.241
ANYBODY GOT
A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

28:29.275 --> 28:30.843
- NO.

28:30.877 --> 28:31.844
- NO.

28:31.878 --> 28:33.846
- [laughs]

28:35.114 --> 28:37.116
- GLAD TO HEAR IT.

28:37.149 --> 28:38.985
HOW ABOUT YOU?

28:39.018 --> 28:41.821
- * I NEED YOUR HOT STUFF

28:41.854 --> 28:42.889
* I NEED YOUR

28:42.922 --> 28:45.324
* HOT STUFF

28:45.357 --> 28:47.059
* HOT STUFF

28:47.093 --> 28:48.828
- [snickers]

28:48.861 --> 28:51.397
- THANK YOU. THAT GOES
OUT TO JEROME, MY BELOVED.

28:51.430 --> 28:53.966
YOU'RE THE ONLY HOT STUFF
I'LL EVER NEED, BABY.

28:54.000 --> 28:56.502
- THANKS, SWEETIE.
YOU'RE MY HOT STUFF TOO, BABY.

28:56.535 --> 28:59.138
[cheers and applause]

28:59.171 --> 29:01.140
- THAT WAS, UH--

29:01.173 --> 29:02.942
THAT WAS SO MOVING.

29:02.975 --> 29:04.410
WASN'T THAT MOVING?

29:04.443 --> 29:06.913
- LIKE A CASE OF DYSENTERY.

29:06.946 --> 29:08.815
- WELL, I THINK
IT TAKES REAL COURAGE

29:08.848 --> 29:12.118
TO STAND UP THERE
AND PROCLAIM YOUR LOVE,

29:12.151 --> 29:15.087
OFF-KEY.

29:15.121 --> 29:16.856
- I GOTTA GET GOING.

29:16.889 --> 29:18.290
- BUT YOU JUST GOT HERE.

29:18.324 --> 29:22.094
- YOU SAID LET'S GET TOGETHER,
AND WE DID.

29:22.128 --> 29:26.265
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF,
MICHAEL.

29:29.568 --> 29:31.537
[overlapping chatter]

29:31.570 --> 29:34.340
- * BEN, THE TWO OF US

29:34.373 --> 29:38.945
* NEED LOOK NO MORE
[feedback from mic]

29:38.978 --> 29:44.350
* WE'VE BOTH FOUND
WHAT WE WERE LOOKING FOR *

29:44.383 --> 29:46.018
- [gasps]

29:46.052 --> 29:50.823
- * WITH A FRIEND
TO CALL MY OWN *

29:50.857 --> 29:54.593
* I'LL NEVER BE ALONE

29:54.626 --> 29:57.964
* AND YOU MY FRIEND WILL SEE

29:57.997 --> 30:01.868
* YOU'VE GOT A FRIEND IN ME

30:01.901 --> 30:08.841
*

30:10.943 --> 30:12.912
- YOU KNOW, I FOUND OUT
A LOT ABOUT YOU

30:12.945 --> 30:14.380
IN THE LAST FEW DAYS.

30:14.413 --> 30:16.883
- LIKE WHAT?

30:16.916 --> 30:18.951
- YOU CAN'T PLAY BASKETBALL.

30:18.985 --> 30:22.154
AND YOU CAN'T SING!
- [laughs]

30:22.188 --> 30:24.590
IT'S PRETTY AMAZING
HOW UNTALENTED I AM, ISN'T IT?

30:24.623 --> 30:27.559
- I DID NOT SAY THAT.

30:27.593 --> 30:30.863
ALL RIGHT, I ADMIT
IT TOOK A LOT OF COURAGE

30:30.897 --> 30:34.500
TO GET UP THERE.

30:34.533 --> 30:38.938
HELL, IT TOOK FUCKING BALLS.

30:38.971 --> 30:40.339
- WELL, I TOLD YOU.

30:40.372 --> 30:41.373
I KNOW WHAT I WANT,

30:41.407 --> 30:43.175
AND I'LL DO ANYTHING
TO GET IT.

30:43.209 --> 30:46.345
- YOU MEAN ME?
- YEAH, I MEAN YOU.

30:46.378 --> 30:49.515
- AH.

31:00.126 --> 31:02.962
ALL RIGHT, TELL YOU WHAT.

31:02.995 --> 31:06.065
DINNER, TOMORROW NIGHT.
MY PLACE.

31:06.098 --> 31:09.401
I WILL MAKE YOU A CHICKEN SATAY
WITH PAD THAI NOODLES

31:09.435 --> 31:12.404
THAT WILL MAKE YOU WEEP.

31:12.438 --> 31:14.006
- COOL.

31:14.040 --> 31:15.607
SHIT!

31:15.641 --> 31:17.376
- WHAT?

31:17.409 --> 31:18.577
- I PROMISED MY MOTHER
I'D HAVE DINNER

31:18.610 --> 31:21.247
WITH HER AND MY UNCLE VIC.

31:21.280 --> 31:22.248
- SOME OTHER TIME, THEN.

31:22.281 --> 31:24.116
- NO.

31:24.150 --> 31:26.618
NO.

31:26.652 --> 31:32.258
DINNER, TOMORROW NIGHT.

31:32.291 --> 31:34.426
[church bells toll]

31:34.460 --> 31:37.329
[thunder rumbles]

31:46.605 --> 31:48.574
- HELLO, REVEREND.

31:50.676 --> 31:55.181
I JUST CAME IN FOR
A FEW QUIET MOMENTS OF SOLACE.

31:55.214 --> 31:56.582
PRAYER.

31:56.615 --> 32:00.352
- WELL,
DON'T LET ME DISTURB YOU.

32:00.386 --> 32:03.222
- YOU SEE,
I HAVE THIS TERRIBLE BURDEN.

32:06.492 --> 32:08.160
- AND WHAT IS THAT?

32:08.194 --> 32:10.429
- WELL, MY MOTHER
RECENTLY DISCOVERED

32:10.462 --> 32:13.032
THAT I'M A HOMOSEXUAL.

32:13.065 --> 32:15.301
AND...

32:15.334 --> 32:19.505
SHE THINKS I'M GOING TO HELL.

32:19.538 --> 32:21.440
- THAT IS A PROBLEM.

32:21.473 --> 32:23.709
- BUT WHAT SHE DOESN'T KNOW

32:23.742 --> 32:27.713
IS THAT SO IS HER MINISTER.

32:27.746 --> 32:29.715
NOT ONLY THAT--

32:29.748 --> 32:34.086
AND THIS IS THE PART
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA BELIEVE--

32:34.120 --> 32:38.057
I'VE ACTUALLY HAD HIM.
MYSELF.

32:38.090 --> 32:39.625
DOWN ON ALL FOURS,

32:39.658 --> 32:40.626
SQUEALING LIKE A PIG.

32:40.659 --> 32:44.330
- I DON'T THINK
THIS IS THE TIME OR THE PLACE

32:44.363 --> 32:46.165
TO BE HAVING
THIS KIND OF DISCUSSION.

32:46.198 --> 32:48.167
- WHAT WOULD SHE SAY
IF SHE KNEW

32:48.200 --> 32:50.236
HER MAN OF GOD
WAS AT THE BATHS

32:50.269 --> 32:54.306
TAKING IT UP THE ASS?

32:54.340 --> 32:59.311
- I UNDERSTAND YOUR FEELINGS
OF ANGER, OF PAIN.

32:59.345 --> 33:03.215
BUT THEY HAVE NOTHING TO DO
WITH ME OR THIS CHURCH.

33:03.249 --> 33:06.118
THEY HAVE TO DO
WITH YOU AND YOUR MOTHER.

33:06.152 --> 33:09.788
- YOU DON'T KNOW SHIT
ABOUT MY MOTHER.

33:09.821 --> 33:12.724
- I KNOW A LOT MORE THAN YOU.

33:12.758 --> 33:15.027
'CAUSE I SPEND TIME WITH HER.

33:15.061 --> 33:18.164
AND I TALK TO HER,
AND I TRY TO OFFER COMFORT.

33:18.197 --> 33:20.632
- BY TELLING HER THAT
I'M GOING TO BURN IN HELL?

33:20.666 --> 33:24.503
- I DON'T TEACH THAT LESSON.

33:24.536 --> 33:27.306
I TEACH LOVE.

33:27.339 --> 33:28.507
I TEACH TRUTH.

33:28.540 --> 33:30.609
- THE TRUTH
IS YOU'RE A GODDAMN LIAR.

33:30.642 --> 33:32.778
- BRIAN,
IF YOU WANT TO BETRAY ME,

33:32.811 --> 33:35.447
IF THAT'S
WHAT YOU NEED TO DO,

33:35.481 --> 33:39.085
YOU DO IT.

33:39.118 --> 33:41.553
BUT I KNOW
WHO I HAVE TO ANSWER TO.

33:41.587 --> 33:45.791
AND IT ISN'T YOU.

33:45.824 --> 33:49.628
NOW GET
THE FUCK OUT OF MY CHURCH.

33:53.232 --> 33:55.367
- SO WHICH PIECE
OF WHIMSICAL FICTION

33:55.401 --> 33:58.570
WOULD YOU PREFER,
SONNY BOY?

33:58.604 --> 34:00.472
GRIMM'S FAIRY TALES?

34:00.506 --> 34:01.707
OR THE BIBLE?

34:01.740 --> 34:03.209
- IF YOU'RE GOING TO BE STRUCK
BY LIGHTNING,

34:03.242 --> 34:04.410
I'D APPRECIATE IT
IF YOU DO IT

34:04.443 --> 34:05.811
WHEN GUS AND I
AREN'T AROUND.

34:05.844 --> 34:08.214
- THAT'S ALL IT IS,
IT'S A BOOK.

34:08.247 --> 34:09.381
FULL OF FAIRY TALES MADE UP

34:09.415 --> 34:10.749
BY A BUNCH
OF TRIBAL HASH-HEADS.

34:10.782 --> 34:14.253
THE WORLD'S BEEN KILLING ITSELF
OVER IT EVER SINCE.

34:14.286 --> 34:15.821
- SO WHO'S THE LATEST VICTIM?

34:15.854 --> 34:18.557
YOUR MOTHER'S MINISTER?

34:18.590 --> 34:19.858
- "YE SHALL KNOW THE TRUTH

34:19.891 --> 34:21.560
AND THE TRUTH SHALL
MAKE YOU FREE."

34:21.593 --> 34:24.230
- THE TRUTH ACCORDING
TO SAINT BRIAN?

34:24.263 --> 34:25.664
- IT'S JOHN 8:32.

34:25.697 --> 34:27.833
- WOW, I'M IMPRESSED.

34:27.866 --> 34:29.735
SO WHAT
DO YOU HOPE TO ACCOMPLISH

34:29.768 --> 34:32.771
WITH YOUR TRUTH?

34:32.804 --> 34:35.174
YOU'LL DESTROY HIM, IN WHICH
CASE YOU'RE NO DIFFERENT

34:35.207 --> 34:36.575
THAN THE SO-CALLED
GOOD CHRISTIANS

34:36.608 --> 34:38.310
YOU PURPORT TO DESPISE.

34:38.344 --> 34:40.579
- DOESN'T MOMMY TALK NICE?

34:40.612 --> 34:43.615
ALL THOSE BIG WORDS.

34:43.649 --> 34:44.716
SHE HAS A RIGHT TO KNOW.

34:44.750 --> 34:45.717
- WHAT, THAT HE'S GAY?

34:45.751 --> 34:49.855
SO HOW COME YOU NEVER
TOLD HER ABOUT YOURSELF?

34:49.888 --> 34:52.658
- BECAUSE MY PRIVATE LIFE IS
NONE OF HER GODDAMN BUSINESS.

34:52.691 --> 34:55.461
RIGHT?
- NEITHER IS HER MINISTER'S.

34:55.494 --> 34:57.863
SO WHY TELL HER?

34:57.896 --> 35:03.569
I MEAN, WHY TAKE AWAY
THE ONE THING SHE'S GOT?

35:03.602 --> 35:05.571
- [sighs]

35:06.638 --> 35:08.740
- DO YOU THINK I MADE ENOUGH?

35:08.774 --> 35:11.277
- THAT DEPENDS ON
WHAT YOU MEAN BY "ENOUGH."

35:11.310 --> 35:13.445
IF YOU MEAN ENOUGH
FOR THE ENTIRE POPULATION

35:13.479 --> 35:14.480
OF THE WESTERN HEMISPHERE,

35:14.513 --> 35:17.683
THEN, YEAH,
YOU'VE MADE ENOUGH.

35:17.716 --> 35:19.885
NOW RELAX, WILL YOU?
- RELAX?

35:19.918 --> 35:22.221
MY SON IS BRINGING
SOMEONE HOME TO MEET US

35:22.254 --> 35:24.256
WITHOUT MY EVEN ASKING.

35:24.290 --> 35:26.625
HUH?
AT HIS REQUEST.

35:26.658 --> 35:28.594
REMEMBER THE LAST TIME
THAT HAPPENED?

35:28.627 --> 35:30.529
- UH...
- IT NEVER HAS.

35:30.562 --> 35:34.366
SO THIS COULD BE THE ONE.

35:34.400 --> 35:38.837
THE GUY HE WANTS
TO GROW OLD WITH.

35:38.870 --> 35:39.938
- WOULDN'T IT BE A KICKER

35:39.971 --> 35:41.640
IF BRIAN WALKED
THROUGH THAT DOOR?

35:41.673 --> 35:43.742
- YEAH, MAYBE YOU NEED
TO GET YOUR MEDS ADJUSTED.

35:43.775 --> 35:44.743
- [chuckles]
[door opens]

35:44.776 --> 35:46.578
- MA, UNCLE VIC?

35:46.612 --> 35:47.646
- OH, THEY'RE HERE.
- GOD, HE'S HERE.

35:47.679 --> 35:49.915
- ALL RIGHT.
- VIC, THEY'RE HERE.

35:49.948 --> 35:50.916
ALL RIGHT.

35:50.949 --> 35:54.720
SWEETHEART!
HI, BABY.

35:54.753 --> 35:59.525
- YOU REMEMBER BEN.

35:59.558 --> 36:01.627
- SURE.

36:01.660 --> 36:03.795
HI, BEN.
- HEY.

36:03.829 --> 36:06.698
- HI.
- AND THIS IS MY UNCLE VIC.

36:06.732 --> 36:08.234
- IT'S A PLEASURE
TO MEET YOU, BEN.

36:08.267 --> 36:11.403
- SAME HERE.

36:11.437 --> 36:13.272
- OH, UH,
THESE ARE FOR YOU.

36:13.305 --> 36:14.740
- WELL, THANK YOU.

36:14.773 --> 36:17.175
THEY'RE LOVELY.

36:18.877 --> 36:20.412
- WELL, ARE WE JUST GONNA
STAND HERE?

36:20.446 --> 36:23.382
COME ON IN.

36:31.923 --> 36:34.693
- MOM.

36:34.726 --> 36:37.696
IMAGINE FINDING YOU HERE.

36:37.729 --> 36:40.732
- I'M PRAYING, BRIAN.

36:40.766 --> 36:43.235
- FOR MY SOUL?

36:43.269 --> 36:45.737
- I ALWAYS INCLUDE YOU
IN MY PRAYERS.

36:45.771 --> 36:48.740
- WHAT A PAL.

37:01.287 --> 37:03.289
[clears throat]

37:07.759 --> 37:10.696
[clears throat loudly]

37:14.032 --> 37:17.403
- [clears throat]

37:17.436 --> 37:19.338
NOW THEN, WHAT DO YOU WANT?

37:19.371 --> 37:20.339
- WELL, THERE'S SOMETHING
I THOUGHT

37:20.372 --> 37:22.408
YOU MIGHT LIKE TO HEAR.

37:22.441 --> 37:25.577
AND THIS SEEMED
LIKE THE PERFECT SETTING.

37:25.611 --> 37:30.782
- I HOPE YOU'VE COME
TO ASK FORGIVENESS.

37:30.816 --> 37:32.684
- NOT EXACTLY.

37:32.718 --> 37:35.687
- IT'S THE ONLY SALVATION
THERE IS.

37:35.721 --> 37:39.591
- WHAT ABOUT
THE SALVATION ARMY?

37:42.093 --> 37:45.831
- YOU'VE ALWAYS THOUGHT
YOU WERE SO SMART, SO CLEVER,

37:45.864 --> 37:49.301
SO MUCH BETTER
THAN EVERYBODY ELSE.

37:49.335 --> 37:51.503
WELL, ALL THE CLEVERNESS
IN THIS WORLD

37:51.537 --> 37:53.372
ISN'T GOING TO HELP YOU.
- SAVE IT, MOM,

37:53.405 --> 37:56.308
FOR YOUR FAG-FREE AFTERLIFE.

37:56.342 --> 37:59.845
- OH. ALL RIGHT.

37:59.878 --> 38:02.748
GO AHEAD, MOCK ME.

38:02.781 --> 38:07.052
MOCK MY FAITH, MOCK GOD.

38:07.085 --> 38:09.888
YOU'RE NO DIFFERENT
THAN YOUR FATHER.

38:09.921 --> 38:12.891
HE USED TO MOCK ME TOO.

38:12.924 --> 38:15.894
HE CALLED ME A SAINT.

38:15.927 --> 38:18.096
HE SAID I WAS
AS STONE-COLD AS ONE.

38:18.129 --> 38:20.432
- [laughs]

38:21.967 --> 38:23.735
- WELL, IT'S HARD TO
LOVE A MAN

38:23.769 --> 38:28.540
WHO'S NEVER GIVEN YOU
A KIND WORD IN 30 YEARS,

38:28.574 --> 38:32.043
WHO'D RATHER SPEND TIME
WITH HIS FRIENDS DRINKING

38:32.077 --> 38:33.679
THAN WITH ME.

38:33.712 --> 38:35.947
HE NEVER CARED
ABOUT HIS FAMILY.

38:35.981 --> 38:39.351
HE DIDN'T EVEN WANT ME
TO HAVE YOU.

38:39.385 --> 38:41.920
- I KNOW THE STORY.

38:41.953 --> 38:43.455
- YOU MAY HAVE HEARD IT,

38:43.489 --> 38:44.990
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW IT.

38:45.023 --> 38:47.826
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW I HAD
TO PUT UP WITH HIS ABUSE,

38:47.859 --> 38:50.396
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW I HAD
TO PROTECT YOU FROM HIM.

38:50.429 --> 38:53.365
YOU DON'T KNOW
HOW I HAD TO LET HIM

38:53.399 --> 38:56.635
HIT ME INSTEAD OF YOU.

38:56.668 --> 39:00.105
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT,
DO YOU?

39:00.138 --> 39:03.108
- I DON'T WANT TO HEAR THAT.

39:03.141 --> 39:07.746
- NO, COURSE NOT.

39:07.779 --> 39:12.451
YOU CAN'T BE BOTHERED.
YOU NEVER COULD.

39:12.484 --> 39:13.752
'CAUSE YOU'RE SELFISH.

39:13.785 --> 39:16.655
- THAT'S NOT TRUE.

39:16.688 --> 39:21.527
- I'M SORRY TO TELL YOU, DEAR,
BUT IT IS.

39:21.560 --> 39:25.831
ALL YOU EVER CARED
ABOUT IS YOURSELF.

39:25.864 --> 39:31.737
I CAN'T DEPEND ON YOU ANY MORE
THAN I COULD ON HIM.

39:31.770 --> 39:34.540
BUT THERE IS SOMEONE
I CAN COUNT ON,

39:34.573 --> 39:39.144
NO MATTER WHAT.

39:39.177 --> 39:41.647
- LET ME GUESS--

39:41.680 --> 39:46.618
REVEREND TOM.

39:46.652 --> 39:51.557
- GOD.

39:51.590 --> 39:55.060
GOD WILL ALWAYS BE THERE
FOR ME.

39:55.093 --> 39:59.498
GOD WILL NEVER LET ME DOWN.

40:01.633 --> 40:05.771
WHO CAN YOU SAY THAT ABOUT?

40:11.943 --> 40:13.879
[upbeat music]

40:13.912 --> 40:17.015
- WELL, MY MOM NEVER DID
ANYTHING HALF-ASSED.

40:17.048 --> 40:19.084
SHE COULDN'T
JUST JOIN PFLAG, RIGHT?

40:19.117 --> 40:20.919
SHE HAD TO BE
THE CHAPTER PRESIDENT.

40:20.952 --> 40:23.221
- SOUNDS FAMILIAR.

40:23.254 --> 40:25.524
- I BET YOU TWO'D
HAVE A LOT IN COMMON, MA.

40:25.557 --> 40:27.759
- UH-HUH.

40:27.793 --> 40:31.129
ANYBODY HUNGRY?
I AM.

40:31.162 --> 40:34.132
[jazzy big band music]

40:34.165 --> 40:39.037
*

40:39.070 --> 40:43.008
- YOU NEED ANY HELP?
- NOPE.

40:44.710 --> 40:46.978
- BEN'S AWESOME, ISN'T HE?
- AWESOME.

40:47.012 --> 40:49.080
WHERE'S
MY GODDAMN CHEESE GRATER?

40:54.252 --> 40:56.221
- I LIKE HIM, MA.
I LIKE HIM A LOT.

40:56.254 --> 40:59.558
- I KNOW YOU DO, SWEETHEART.
I LIKE HIM TOO.

40:59.591 --> 41:00.959
HE'S HANDSOME,
CHARMING, SMART.

41:00.992 --> 41:04.229
OBVIOUSLY WORKS OUT
MORE THAN ONCE A WEEK.

41:04.262 --> 41:06.998
I JUST DON'T LIKE HIM
FOR YOU.

41:11.069 --> 41:13.705
AND FRANKLY I DON'T
APPRECIATE YOU AMBUSHING ME.

41:13.739 --> 41:15.040
- I DID NOT AMBUSH YOU.

41:15.073 --> 41:16.608
- YOU KNOW
HOW I FEEL ABOUT HIM.

41:16.642 --> 41:18.610
I MADE IT PERFECTLY CLEAR.

41:18.644 --> 41:19.978
AND YET YOU DIDN'T
EVEN BOTHER TO TELL ME

41:20.011 --> 41:20.979
YOU WERE BRINGING HIM.

41:21.012 --> 41:22.648
- I DON'T NEED YOUR PERMISSION.

41:22.681 --> 41:24.616
- THIS IS STILL MY HOUSE.

41:24.650 --> 41:29.688
AND IN MY HOUSE,
YOU STILL SAY "MOTHER, MAY I?"

41:29.721 --> 41:33.625
- I LOVE HIM, MA.

41:33.659 --> 41:35.661
THAT'S THE REALITY.

41:35.694 --> 41:39.030
AND YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO LIVE WITH IT.

41:42.167 --> 41:44.703
- [laughs]
- GOD, I MISS NEW YORK.

41:44.736 --> 41:45.637
- MM-HM.

41:45.671 --> 41:47.272
- I LIVED THERE FOR 12 YEARS,
YOU KNOW.

41:47.305 --> 41:49.675
WHAT'S THAT BAR ON
THE UPPER WEST SIDE?

41:49.708 --> 41:50.842
"THE WORKS."

41:50.876 --> 41:52.277
YOU EVER GO THERE?

41:52.310 --> 41:53.745
- OH.
WHAT, ARE YOU KIDDING?

41:53.779 --> 41:57.015
I GREW UP RIGHT
AROUND THE CORNER.

41:57.048 --> 42:01.987
- SO HOW LONG
YOU BEEN POSITIVE, BEN?

42:03.755 --> 42:04.823
- MOTHER.

42:04.856 --> 42:06.224
- I'D JUST LIKE TO KNOW.

42:06.257 --> 42:08.627
- THAT'S OKAY.
I'M FINE WITH IT.

42:08.660 --> 42:10.195
FIVE YEARS.

42:10.228 --> 42:11.663
- WHAT'S YOUR T-CELL COUNT?

42:11.697 --> 42:14.132
[silverware clatters]
- UH, IT'S 600.

42:14.165 --> 42:16.001
- EVER BEEN HOSPITALIZED?

42:16.034 --> 42:17.035
- NO, NOT YET.
[raps on table]

42:17.068 --> 42:18.069
KNOCK WOOD.

42:18.103 --> 42:20.005
- VIRAL LOAD?

42:20.038 --> 42:22.040
- UNDETECTABLE.

42:22.073 --> 42:23.341
- ON THE COCKTAIL?

42:23.374 --> 42:24.876
- ANTI-VIRALS.

42:24.910 --> 42:29.848
- WHAT THE FUCK
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

42:29.881 --> 42:34.686
- THIS IS THE REALITY,
SWEETHEART.

42:34.720 --> 42:38.990
AND YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO LIVE WITH IT.

42:49.735 --> 42:52.971
GARLIC BREAD?

42:55.240 --> 42:58.209
[energetic dance music]

42:58.243 --> 43:06.117
*

43:07.753 --> 43:09.821
- IT'S GREAT
THAT YOU'RE OUT IN THE WORLD,

43:09.855 --> 43:12.023
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE NOT LETTING
IT GET YOU DOWN.

43:12.057 --> 43:13.825
- I WISH SOMETHING
WOULD GET IT DOWN.

43:13.859 --> 43:15.093
- HEY.

43:15.126 --> 43:16.327
HEY, TED.

43:16.361 --> 43:18.363
LISTEN, MAN, I'M SORRY
ABOUT THE OTHER NIGHT.

43:18.396 --> 43:21.366
- I KNOW.
HOW'S LULU?

43:21.399 --> 43:25.036
- TURNS OUT SHE ATE
A PAIR OF MY SHORTS.

